00:23:13,820 --> 00:23:16,060
I'm fine.

256
00:23:16,060 --> 00:23:19,860
I'll be back at school tomorrow.

257
00:23:51,990 --> 00:23:54,740
 Milk tea can be twice as sweet, 

258
00:23:54,740 --> 00:23:59,600
 but the bitterness in Jing Xi Chi's eyes was even stronger. 

259
00:24:30,440 --> 00:24:33,140
Don't go to school the day after tomorrow.

260
00:24:33,140 --> 00:24:36,840
I've arranged for you to attend a training program at Tonglin City Sports School.

261
00:24:36,840 --> 00:24:39,940
Coach Li will take you there. 
    

262
00:24:47,860 --> 00:24:51,423
 I heard the sports university in Tonglin is quite good. 

263
00:24:51,423 --> 00:24:54,910
 I'm near the place. Let me check it out for you first. 

264
00:24:54,910 --> 00:24:56,570
 Got it. 

265
00:24:57,225 --> 00:24:59,600
   

266
00:25:02,570 --> 00:25:04,710
My father arranged this for me.

267
00:26:02,390 --> 00:26:03,870
Jing Xi Chi!

268
00:26:03,870 --> 00:26:06,680
You've got to hold on until the very end.

269
00:26:16,420 --> 00:26:19,180
   

270
00:27:15,100 --> 00:27:17,980
No matter how sad you are, you can't just give up on your legs.

271
00:27:34,540 --> 00:27:39,050
What's the use of my legs now?

272
00:27:44,260 --> 00:27:46,430
I failed the physical exam.

273
00:27:48,250 --> 00:27:50,190
I didn't make it.

274
00:27:55,020 --> 00:27:57,480
I really tried my best,

275
00:27:59,100 --> 00:28:01,740
but my legs are still like this.

276
00:28:05,240 --> 00:28:14,820
Maybe in life, there really are things that can't be solved just by working hard.

277
00:28:19,230 --> 00:28:20,860
Cong.

278
00:28:29,710 --> 00:28:32,810
I really tried so hard...

279
00:28:34,870 --> 00:28:37,440
So why do I still have regrets?

280
00:28:48,090 --> 00:28:49,910
You know...

281
00:28:51,570 --> 00:28:53,470
Actually...

282
00:28:56,080 --> 00:28:58,780
It wasn't supposed to be my dad's shift that day.

283
00:29:00,950 --> 00:29:03,290
Do you know why he switched shifts?

284
00:29:09,430 --> 00:29:13,920
He had arranged a meeting with a sports school coach for me.

285
00:29:14,990 --> 00:29:25,530
 He went to ask if they could give me a chance to transfer and continue playing football. 

286
00:29:41,200 --> 00:29:46,870
If only my father had given up on me sooner...

287
00:29:47,990 --> 00:29:50,820
If only I hadn't been so stubborn...

288
00:29:53,190 --> 00:29:56,870
If I had realized this earlier,

289
00:29:59,020 --> 00:30:04,600
would my father still have gotten into that accident?

290
00:30:16,330 --> 00:30:18,400
It'll all pass eventually.

291
00:30:21,390 --> 00:30:27,960
 Many people say that facing loss is the true beginning of growth. 

292
00:30:27,960 --> 00:30:31,240
 I hate this way of romanticizing loss. 

293
00:30:31,240 --> 00:30:33,666
 Loss is just loss. 

294
00:30:33,666 --> 00:30:37,540
 If growth comes at the cost of losing something, it's unfair. 

295
00:30:38,920 --> 00:30:46,230
 Later on, Uncle Jing was honored, becoming a hero in everyone's eyes. 

296
00:30:46,230 --> 00:30:51,470
 But for Xi Chi, all he faced was still just loss. 

297
00:30:51,470 --> 00:30:57,327
 But what he chose to do was exactly what Uncle Jing had done. 

298
00:30:57,327 --> 00:30:59,540
 He stepped up to hold the family together. 

299
00:31:24,990 --> 00:31:26,610
Mom.

300
00:31:39,470 --> 00:31:45,610
I have an early meeting tomorrow, so I might leave home early.

301
00:31:45,610 --> 00:31:48,740
I washed your school uniform for you.

302
00:31:48,740 --> 00:31:53,890
If it's not dry, just use the hairdryer yourself.

303
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:58,130
Mom.

304
00:32:00,290 --> 00:32:02,240
I'm sorry.

305
00:32:02,240 --> 00:32:04,410
I know I've let you down.

306
00:32:07,150 --> 00:32:09,090
Silly boy.

307
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:12,910
You will always be my pride.

308
00:32:14,100 --> 00:32:16,140
And your father's too.

309
00:32:45,740 --> 00:32:48,470
 Today is Uncle Jing's birthday. 

310
00:32:48,470 --> 00:32:53,000
 Xi Chi kept his window shut the entire day. 

311
00:32:53,000 --> 00:33:01,190
 Football, family, and the things he cherished most are all slipping away. 

312
00:33:01,770 --> 00:33:07,100
 Even the light in his heart seemed to have been taken too. 

313
00:33:08,630 --> 00:33:13,390
 Opening the window would let sunlight into the room. 

314
00:33:14,820 --> 00:33:20,250
 But how could that light find its way into his heart? 

315
00:34:38,870 --> 00:34:40,990
Sorry.

316
00:34:40,990 --> 00:34:45,020
I didn't go to school because I had something to deal with.

317
00:34:48,860 --> 00:34:50,390
Here, take this.

318
00:34:50,390 --> 00:34:53,690
You can listen to it when you're feeling tired.

319
00:34:55,170 --> 00:34:57,070
Is everything okay?

320
00:34:58,160 --> 00:35:00,670
I'm going to start studying.

321
00:35:03,700 --> 00:35:05,350
Let's go.

322
00:35:13,980 --> 00:35:16,020
   

323
00:35:16,020 --> 00:35:18,100
 Senior year's exhausting... and honestly, 

324
00:35:18,100 --> 00:35:21,700
 everyone's just handling it in their own weird way. 
   

325
00:35:21,700 --> 00:35:23,210
Abandon. Abandon.

326
00:35:23,210 --> 00:35:24,930
A, B, A, N, D, O, N.

327
00:35:24,930 --> 00:35:27,570
Abandon. Abandon.

328
00:35:27,570 --> 00:35:29,680
Can you stop acting crazy?

329
00:35:29,680 --> 00:35:33,720
You always start with the word "abandon," then you want to abandon your studies!

330
00:35:33,720 --> 00:35:35,540
It's bad luck!

331
00:35:38,660 --> 00:35:43,580
Stay calm, stay peaceful, and go with the flow.

332
00:35:43,580 --> 00:35:47,300
Mindset determines everything.

333
00:35:57,540 --> 00:36:03,020
 Among all the strange things, the strangest was definitely Jing Xi Chi. 

334
00:36:04,120 --> 00:36:07,850
 He went through roughly three stages. 

335
00:36:09,310 --> 00:36:13,750
 First stage. He turned into a studying machine. 

336
00:36:17,840 --> 00:36:23,210
 I knew this was the only way he could temporarily push aside thoughts about Uncle Jing. 

337
00:36:23,210 --> 00:36:27,990
 However, I didn't expect him to push himself this hard. 

338
00:36:27,990 --> 00:36:29,990
Exactly.

339
00:36:29,990 --> 00:36:32,240
I don't know what triggered Xi Chi.

340
00:36:32,240 --> 00:36:35,120
He studies until midnight every day.

341
00:36:36,020 --> 00:36:40,290
Yi Fan. You can't let him continue this. His body won't take it.

342
00:36:40,290 --> 00:36:42,180
I know.

343
00:36:42,180 --> 00:36:45,700
I'm worried too. Now, he barely talks anymore.

344
00:36:45,700 --> 00:36:48,210
I have no idea what's going on in his head.

345
00:36:48,210 --> 00:36:50,420
Negative angle and zero angle...

346
00:36:51,540 --> 00:36:56,090
 When it came to the second stage, he basically lost it. 

347
00:37:00,960 --> 00:37:05,100
You're not paying attention in my class anymore.

348
00:37:05,100 --> 00:37:07,240
Come to my office after school.

349
00:37:18,640 --> 00:37:23,580
 Third stage: A legendary top student was born. 

350
00:37:23,580 --> 00:37:27,460
 Everyone said he was acting strange, and that this wasn't the right way to cope. 

351
00:37:27,460 --> 00:37:32,090
 However, the changes on the ranking board told a different story. 

352
00:37:37,660 --> 00:37:39,630
Take a look.

353
00:37:42,830 --> 00:37:45,000
Jing Xi Chi. You did pretty well.

354
00:37:45,000 --> 00:37:46,280
You're only five ranks behind me now.

355
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:48,116
Really?

356
00:37:48,116 --> 00:37:50,590
- That high? 
 - Didn't you check?

357
00:37:51,370 --> 00:37:52,770
No.

358
00:37:52,770 --> 00:37:56,430
It doesn't mean anything until the final results.

359
00:37:58,160 --> 00:38:00,240
This year, the Chinese New Year holiday lasts until the eighth.

360
00:38:00,240 --> 00:38:01,940
Are you going back to Sishui?

361
00:38:01,940 --> 00:38:05,156
No. My mother is working the night shift on Chinese New Year's Eve.

362
00:38:05,156 --> 00:38:08,100
I'll probably stay in the hospital with her.

363
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:11,450
Robot, what about you?

364
00:38:12,520 --> 00:38:15,010
- She's asking you. 
 - We'll see.

365
00:38:27,660 --> 00:38:29,190
Here.

366
00:38:30,040 --> 00:38:31,390
Eat more.

367
00:38:31,390 --> 00:38:33,049
All right, Mom. Don't worry about me.

368
00:38:33,049 --> 00:38:35,425
Why does everyone decide to give birth during the New Year?

369
00:38:35,425 --> 00:38:37,080
- I know, right? 
 - Li Na.

370
00:38:37,080 --> 00:38:39,367
Hello.

371
00:38:39,367 --> 00:38:40,940
Why are you eating instant noodles during the New Year?

372
00:38:40,940 --> 00:38:42,288
Have some dumplings.

373
00:38:42,288 --> 00:38:44,315
Thank you, Li Na, but it's fine. Our noodles are almost ready.

374
00:38:44,315 --> 00:38:46,500
Dumplings are a must during the New Year.

375
00:38:46,500 --> 00:38:47,725
These are really good.

376
00:38:47,725 --> 00:38:50,170
Eat more so that you have the energy to take care of the patients.

377
00:38:50,170 --> 00:38:51,750
Thank you.

378
00:38:53,020 --> 00:38:55,000
I won't have time to check on you later.

379
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:59,103
If you feel bored, go to Aunt Yi Fan's house.

380
00:38:59,103 --> 00:39:00,838
Aunt Yi Fan is on duty today.

381
00:39:00,838 --> 00:39:03,820
Jing Xi Chi must be home. Go find him.

382
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:09,110
Eat.

383
00:39:47,620 --> 00:39:49,130
What's up?

384
00:39:50,350 --> 00:39:52,070
What are you doing?

385
00:39:54,640 --> 00:39:57,721
I just got back from having dinner at Cong's place.

386
00:39:57,721 --> 00:39:59,000
I have nothing much to do.

387
00:39:59,000 --> 00:40:01,770
I'm planning to go over the final exam papers again.

388
00:40:02,480 --> 00:40:03,976
 What about you? 

389
00:40:03,976 --> 00:40:06,890
 Aren't you at the hospital keeping Aunt Li Na company? 

390
00:40:08,760 --> 00:40:09,990
She's busy.

391
00:40:09,990 --> 00:40:14,080
If I stay there, I'll just distract her, so I came back.

392
00:40:15,280 --> 00:40:16,737
Then get some rest early.

393
00:40:16,737 --> 00:40:18,210
I'm going to do my exercises.

394
00:40:18,210 --> 00:40:21,770
 It's Chinese New Year's Eve. Why are you still studying? 

395
00:40:23,700 --> 00:40:26,160
What else would I do?

396
00:40:26,160 --> 00:40:27,730
I'm hanging up.

397
00:40:47,330 --> 00:40:49,430
Hello? Cong.

398
00:40:49,430 --> 00:40:51,120
What are you doing?

399
00:40:54,320 --> 00:40:56,040
Where's Jing Xi Chi?

400
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:57,872
He's studying at home.

401
00:40:57,872 --> 00:41:00,560
Is he studying at home on New Year's Eve?

402
00:41:00,560 --> 00:41:02,520
That's insane.

403
00:41:03,270 --> 00:41:04,700
- Du Man. 
 - Du Man.

404
00:41:04,700 --> 00:41:06,800
- Happy New Year! 
 - You're here.

405
00:41:06,800 --> 00:41:09,830
- Where's your father? 
 - He went out to play Mahjong.

406
00:41:09,830 --> 00:41:11,950
- Take whatever you want to eat. 
 - No.

407
00:41:11,950 --> 00:41:13,770
Uncle Du already gave me loads of snacks.

408
00:41:13,770 --> 00:41:16,120
I feel bad.

409
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:18,120
That's just how my father is.

410
00:41:18,120 --> 00:41:20,060
He gives away more than he sells.

411
00:41:20,060 --> 00:41:21,852
He's been like this for over ten years. Whatever he touches turns to bad business.

412
00:41:21,852 --> 00:41:24,090
Don't say that about him.

413
00:41:24,090 --> 00:41:26,220
We'll take a few, then.

414
00:41:30,990 --> 00:41:32,390
How many bottles?

415
00:41:32,390 --> 00:41:33,980
Six.

416
00:41:40,620 --> 00:41:42,920
Are you guys drinking?

417
00:41:45,180 --> 00:41:46,170
Is that okay?

418
00:41:46,170 --> 00:41:47,580
Are you 18 already?

419
00:41:47,580 --> 00:41:50,220
Of course.

420
00:41:50,220 --> 00:41:52,720
I turned 18 three months ago.

421
00:41:54,900 --> 00:41:57,330
All right, take them.

422
00:41:58,940 --> 00:42:01,040
- Take my money. 
 - No need. Just take them.

423
00:42:01,040 --> 00:42:03,900
If you don't, we won't come next time.

424
00:42:05,610 --> 00:42:07,600
- Let's go. 
 - Happy New Year.

425
00:42:07,600 --> 00:42:09,340
- Happy New Year. 
 - Happy New Year.

426
00:42:09,340 --> 00:42:11,300
You're just like your father.

