00:42:26,460 --> 00:42:34,060
   

428
00:42:37,820 --> 00:42:40,770
Happy New Year, Robot!

429
00:42:41,720 --> 00:42:42,902
Why are you two here?

430
00:42:42,902 --> 00:42:44,670
My parents are home for the New Year, for once.

431
00:42:44,670 --> 00:42:46,670
I figured I'd give them some space.

